    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cars, carriages, or other nonmotorized wheeled vehicles that include a chassis and are primarily intended to be towed by other vehicles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
